com.intel.fightclub.coach.mediator

Class SessionDataWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.coach.mediator.SessionDataWriter

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class SessionDataWriter
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps the storage lib API so that database read/writes are done in their own thread.
